{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/review/무료-아이폰-마크다운-에디터/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"무료 아이폰 마크다운 에디터","subtitle":null,"date":"2017.01.14","category":"review"},"html":"<h1>bear</h1>\n<p>이 블로그의 글쓰기 시스템은 마크다운을 기반으로 구성되어 있다. 본격적으로 글쓰기를 하기 위해서 모바일 용 마크다운 클라이언트를 찾게 되었다. 여러 앱을 사용해본 결과 앱 아이콘도 깔끔하고 인터페이스도 간결하게 잘 정리되어 있어 bear로 정했다.</p>\n<p>앱을 다운로드 한 뒤 유료 결제를 하면 pdf나 이미지파일로 내보내기도 지원한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 177.91411042944785%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/eb72bf5b71ebc8899f9d96bb5c8484f8/a81b5/20170114_094328000_iOS.webp 163w,\n/static/eb72bf5b71ebc8899f9d96bb5c8484f8/da3ef/20170114_094328000_iOS.webp 325w,\n/static/eb72bf5b71ebc8899f9d96bb5c8484f8/309d5/20170114_094328000_iOS.webp 650w,\n/static/eb72bf5b71ebc8899f9d96bb5c8484f8/78344/20170114_094328000_iOS.webp 975w,\n/static/eb72bf5b71ebc8899f9d96bb5c8484f8/cd45f/20170114_094328000_iOS.webp 1242w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/eb72bf5b71ebc8899f9d96bb5c8484f8/222b7/20170114_094328000_iOS.png 163w,\n/static/eb72bf5b71ebc8899f9d96bb5c8484f8/ff46a/20170114_094328000_iOS.png 325w,\n/static/eb72bf5b71ebc8899f9d96bb5c8484f8/a6d36/20170114_094328000_iOS.png 650w,\n/static/eb72bf5b71ebc8899f9d96bb5c8484f8/e548f/20170114_094328000_iOS.png 975w,\n/static/eb72bf5b71ebc8899f9d96bb5c8484f8/89048/20170114_094328000_iOS.png 1242w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/eb72bf5b71ebc8899f9d96bb5c8484f8/a6d36/20170114_094328000_iOS.png\"\n            alt=\"bear app\"\n            title=\"bear app\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>마크다운 문법을 입력하면 실시간으로 미리보기가 가능하다. 키보드 위에 나오는 툴바로 마크다운 문법을 사용하지 않아도 사용할 수 있다.</p>\n<h2>markdown 설정 켜기</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 177.91411042944785%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/769929cc568494e2a72840053a614f1b/a81b5/20170114_094358000_iOS.webp 163w,\n/static/769929cc568494e2a72840053a614f1b/da3ef/20170114_094358000_iOS.webp 325w,\n/static/769929cc568494e2a72840053a614f1b/309d5/20170114_094358000_iOS.webp 650w,\n/static/769929cc568494e2a72840053a614f1b/78344/20170114_094358000_iOS.webp 975w,\n/static/769929cc568494e2a72840053a614f1b/cd45f/20170114_094358000_iOS.webp 1242w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/769929cc568494e2a72840053a614f1b/222b7/20170114_094358000_iOS.png 163w,\n/static/769929cc568494e2a72840053a614f1b/ff46a/20170114_094358000_iOS.png 325w,\n/static/769929cc568494e2a72840053a614f1b/a6d36/20170114_094358000_iOS.png 650w,\n/static/769929cc568494e2a72840053a614f1b/e548f/20170114_094358000_iOS.png 975w,\n/static/769929cc568494e2a72840053a614f1b/89048/20170114_094358000_iOS.png 1242w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/769929cc568494e2a72840053a614f1b/a6d36/20170114_094358000_iOS.png\"\n            alt=\"bear app\"\n            title=\"bear app\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>설정에서 마크다운 최적화를 토글할 수 있다. 뭐가 달라지는지는 잘 모르겠음.</p>\n<h2>내보내기</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 177.91411042944785%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/281df8b1bcb82ed878edea8742f4a4df/a81b5/20170114_094340000_iOS.webp 163w,\n/static/281df8b1bcb82ed878edea8742f4a4df/da3ef/20170114_094340000_iOS.webp 325w,\n/static/281df8b1bcb82ed878edea8742f4a4df/309d5/20170114_094340000_iOS.webp 650w,\n/static/281df8b1bcb82ed878edea8742f4a4df/78344/20170114_094340000_iOS.webp 975w,\n/static/281df8b1bcb82ed878edea8742f4a4df/cd45f/20170114_094340000_iOS.webp 1242w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/281df8b1bcb82ed878edea8742f4a4df/222b7/20170114_094340000_iOS.png 163w,\n/static/281df8b1bcb82ed878edea8742f4a4df/ff46a/20170114_094340000_iOS.png 325w,\n/static/281df8b1bcb82ed878edea8742f4a4df/a6d36/20170114_094340000_iOS.png 650w,\n/static/281df8b1bcb82ed878edea8742f4a4df/e548f/20170114_094340000_iOS.png 975w,\n/static/281df8b1bcb82ed87